            "type": "patchouli:text",
            "text": "$(li)The Conduit Power actives when you are in contact with rain or water.$(br)$(li)This effect gives to you $(l:patchouli:potions/vanilla/water_breathing)Water Breathing$(/l) making you to don't lose oxygen.$(br)$(li)It gives to you $(l:patchouli:potions/vanilla/night_vision)Night Vision$(/l) allowing you to see clearly underwater or at night.$(br)$(li)Finally it gives to you the $(l)Haste$() effect, allowing you to mine blocks quickly."
        },
